data.name: Tiago Coffee Bar & Kitchen
data.ranking: #7 of 400 Quick Bites in Los Angeles
data.description: Here at Tiago we are committed to serving food with integrity which means we're respectful of sustainability, farmers, farms, the way animals are raised as well as our environment. Almost everything at Tiago is made to order, so you're getting the freshest possible food and coffee. Remember freshly made food takes time to make so be patient. For our meats and produce we use local farmers and producers, the cows are grass fed and when possible no added hormones. Most of our produce is organic and comes from various farms spread out over California. The milk we use for our drinks is all natural and comes from cows that are again hormone free. Most of our coffee roasters use fair trade and/or direct trade which means that you're buying into value that in turn goes directly back to the roasters, the farms and the farmers. We use completely recyclable and bio-degradable products for our to go containers to make up for less waste for our environment. We're on a journey to provide you with quality food and want to thank you for riding along with us.
